&lt;img src=&#34;https://github.com/ziv-lin/ImMesh_release/raw/main/pics/overview_v7.jpg&#34; style=&#34;margin: -1px 0px 0px 0px&#34; alt=&#34;video&#34; width=&#34;100%&#34; /&gt;
